&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in editing YAML files using &lt;code&gt;vi&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;vim&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;nano&lt;/code&gt;, or your preferred text editor.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supported Environments:
