&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="callout__body"&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Exercise&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Create a workshop directory&lt;/strong&gt;: In your environment create a new directory (e.g., &lt;code&gt;advanced-otel-workshop&lt;/code&gt;). We will refer to this directory as &lt;code&gt;[WORKSHOP]&lt;/code&gt; for the remainder of the workshop.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>